{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.startTime","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>startTime</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>La propiedad <strong><code>Animation.startTime</code></strong> de la interfaz <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"La documentación acerca de este tema no ha sido escrita todavía . ¡Por favor  considera contribuir !\"><code>Animación</code></a> es un valor de punto flotante de doble precisión que indica el tiempo programado en el que debe comenzar la reproducción de una animación.</span></span></p>\n\n<p>El&nbsp; <strong>start time</strong> <strong>(tiempo de inicio)</strong> es el valor de tiempo de su <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"La documentación acerca de este tema no ha sido escrita todavía . ¡Por favor  considera contribuir !\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code></a>cuando su objetivo <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> está programado para comenzar la reproducción. <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>El </span></span><strong>start time</strong> <strong>(tiempo de inicio)</strong><span lang=\"es\"><span> de una animación inicialmente no está resuelto (lo que significa que es <code>null</code> porque no tiene valor).</span></span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"<span class=\"highlight-span\">Sintaxis</span>","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>animationStartedWhen</em> = <em>Animation</em>.startTime;\n\n<em>Animation</em>.startTime = <em>newStartTime</em>;</pre>","titleAsText":"Sintaxis"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Un número de punto flotante que representa el tiempo actual en milisegundos, o nulo si no se establece ningún valor de&nbsp; tiempo. Puede leer este valor para determinar en qué momento está establecido el punto de inicio, y puede modificarlo para que la animación comience en un momento diferente.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En el ejemplo <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/zxYexJ?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Running on Web Animations API&nbsp;example</a>, podemos sincronizar todos los nuevos gatos animados dándoles el mismo tiempo de inicio <code>startTime</code> que el gato original:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> catRunning <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"withWAAPI\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">animate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>keyframes<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> timing<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Una función que crea nuevos gatos. */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">addCat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> newCat <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"div\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  newCat<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>classList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"cat\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> newCat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Esta es la función que agrega un gato a la columna WAAPI */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">animateNewCatWithWAAPI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// crea unnuevo gato</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> newCat <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">addCat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Animar a dicho gato con la función \"animate\" de WAAPI</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> newAnimationPlayer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> newCat<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">animate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>keyframes<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> timing<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Establece que el punto de inicio de la animación sea el mismo que el original .cat#withWAAPI</span>\n  newAnimationPlayer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startTime <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> catRunning<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startTime<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Agrega el gato a la pila.</span>\n  WAAPICats<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>newCat<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"<span class=\"highlight-span\"><span class=\"highlight-span\">Especificaciones</span></span>","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-starttime\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'Animation.startTime' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Editor's draft.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"Especificaciones"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.startTime","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"<span class=\"highlight-span\">Ver también</span>","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>Animation.currentTime</code></a> para el tiempo actual de la animación.</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Ver también"}}],"toc":[{"text":"<span class=\"highlight-span\">Sintaxis</span>","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"<span class=\"highlight-span\"><span class=\"highlight-span\">Especificaciones</span></span>","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador"},{"text":"<span class=\"highlight-span\">Ver también</span>","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"La propiedad Animation.startTime de la interfaz Animación es un valor de punto flotante de doble precisión que indica el tiempo programado en el que debe comenzar la reproducción de una animación.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.startTime","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.mozAnimationStartTime","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window.mozAnimationStartTime","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"window.mozAnimationStartTime","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/starttime","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/starttime/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime","title":"Animation.startTime"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.startTime - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}